      <title>麦肯锡前合伙人承认销毁阿片类药物推广工作记录</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/ex-mckinsey-partner-pleads-guilty-destroying-records-about-work-promoting-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦肯锡公司一位前合伙人周五承认妨碍司法公正，因为他销毁了他和该咨询公司向普渡制药提供的关于如何“加速”其阿片类止痛药奥施康定销售的建议的相关记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/ex-mckinsey-partner-pleads-guilty-destroying-records-about-work-promoting-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 17:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
